<p class="MsoNormal">Master asked me to leave my 6PM onwards free... It seems that the time has finally come.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">He has quite have the shy look when he asked me to leave my schedule open for tonight, but knowing things based from our conversation last night, It only meant one thing... Our time has come.<span style="mso-tab-count: 1">            </span></p>

