<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Soon after, as I try to sort things out today, Ushio came to the office to officially congratulate me (she is being a spoiler to the story anyways). We have spoken a few words with one another and she wishes me the best of luck to the things that will arrive to me.</p>

